properties.text: Olympics: As the Games came to the capital for the third time, Britain basked in the glory of hosting a successful event. Britons also celebrated a bumper medal haul, coming third in the table with 29 golds.

Selfies: Photos taken of the user - by the user, have become so popular that in 2013 'selfie' was crowned Oxford Dictionaries' word of the year. The monarch isn't a fan herself... saying she finds the trend 'strange'
1D: A symbol of the times, the band were first created on reality TV show The X Factor. Since forming they have accumulated an estimated combined net wealth of approximately £70million.
